short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirects all debuglogs.org requests to debuglogs.app

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Logs for Signal Messenger are hosted on debuglogs.org. This extension redirects requests to debuglogs.org to debuglogs.app, an unofficial in-browser debuglog viewer.

For more info, check out the source on Github:
https://github.com/greysonp/debuglogs.app
